{"tid":1694594,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"6點 九龍西 旺角 V煞蒙面緊急集合！！","createTime":"2019-11-05T08:24:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T08:48:06.000Z","uid":72602,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ff8f6e06d261ba34ae6c5796903909b4646c31ac","tid":1694594,"uid":72602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:24:05.000Z","msg":"科大同學已經宣告腦幹死亡<br />\n一條年輕生命就咁比警暴政權害死左<br />\n原本佢有大好前途... 有幸福既未來等緊佢<br />\n佢已經無機會成家立室 睇唔到佢既下一代<br />\n亦都同唔到我地煲底相認 光復香港既一日<br />\n我地仲係唔係放工放學仲唔企出黎 飲飲食食<br />\n一早應該三罷抵抗到底 妄想港共政權會跪低<br />\n活生生一條<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人命</span></span>黎架<br />\n唔該今日大家 九龍西 我絕不虛作無聲<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">6點見各位</span></span> <br />\n我地唔可以再容許手足犧牲"},{"pid":"1b90fc6c9436312182b696fa0ed400096febe846","tid":1694594,"uid":72602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:24:26.000Z","msg":"唔該推上去！"},{"pid":"d61234046385087f364b425327b1a1d3cd5cf4e2","tid":1694594,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:24:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de686d9e064062bbd2510257c4990f7967de45f9","tid":1694594,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:25:22.000Z","msg":"力量來自團結，團結來自信念。（Strength through unity, unity through faith）"},{"pid":"faed97b655dbdbefa529179f244e2859a564dabd","tid":1694594,"uid":40606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:25:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj